{"name": "Early Aristocrat", "type": "background", "img": "icons/commodities/treasure/broach-crown-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>Whether you were born to high society or merely appointed to it later in life, you have learned and internalized the customs and manners of the who's-who. Though entreating with other figures of influence can be an exhausting ordeal at times, it's certainly not without its perks.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Skill Proficiency:</strong> Pick one of the following: Culture, Deception, Insight, Intimidation, Perform, Persuasion.</p>\n<p><strong>Other Proficiency:</strong> Pick one of the following:<ul><li>You are proficient in one of the following trades: Art (Choose any Specialization), Entertainment (Singing, Dance, or Musical Instrument), or Subterfuge</li><li>You can speak, read, and write one additional language of your choice.</li></ul></p>\n<p><strong>Background Feature:</strong> @Compendium[undertaking-homebrew.abilities.2BWN854LL0WQ39J3]{Institutional Sway}</p>\n<p><strong>Equipment: </strong>A signet ring and one of the following: a art kit, subterfuge kit, or musical instrument.</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "portion": "early"}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {}, "_id": "GWOPIKU2B4T2KLRQ", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Early Artisan", "type": "background", "img": "icons/skills/trades/textiles-cloth-dye-red.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>You are trained in the way of a particular craft, and have likely made most of your living plying its trade. You may have been sculpted from a young age as an apprentice or taken up the art later in life. Either way, you have developed an eye for quality and the skills to fashion it.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Skill Proficiency:</strong> Pick one of the following: Craft, Culture, Investigation, Persuasion, or Sleight of Hand.</p>\n<p><strong>Trade Proficiency:</strong> Alchemy, Artisan (Choose any Specialization), Smithing, or Tinkering.</p>\n<p><strong>Background Feature:</strong> @Compendium[undertaking-homebrew.abilities.5Z5KEPS9RQKUVCPC]{Eye for Quality}</p>\n<p><strong>Equipment: </strong>A merchant's scale and one artisan kit you are proficient with (excluding the alchemy kit).</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "portion": "early"}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {}, "_id": "QBNIV394WWIIOUS9", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Early Devotee", "type": "background", "img": "icons/environment/people/cleric-orange.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>You have spent a great deal of time living in or around a temple or other community of faith, and the lessons you have taken away from it mean a great deal to you. Though the wider world now calls to you, the faith you've nurtured ever guides you and brings you comfort in trying times.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Skill Proficiency:</strong> Pick one of the following: Culture, Intimidation, Perform, Persuasion, Theology.</p>\n<p><strong>Trade Proficiency:</strong> Art (Choose any Specialization), Botany, Cooking, Entertainment (Singing or Musical Instrument).</p>\n<p><strong>Background Feature:</strong> @Compendium[undertaking-homebrew.abilities.CZKRUMYCK6X1L5WN]{Beseech Providence}</p>\n<p><strong>Equipment: </strong><ul><li>Either an amulet (holy focus) or idol (holy focus).</li><li>One of the following: An art kit, botany kit, cooking kit, or a musical instrument.</li></ul></p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "portion": "early"}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {}, "_id": "64EFYI39SS88H6S2", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Early Militant", "type": "background", "img": "icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>You have spent impactful portions of your life around regions marked by strife. Whether you were instructed in self-defense as a youth or trained as an adult to serve in an army or guardpost, you have acquired the skills to brave the test of combat.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Skill Proficiency:</strong> Pick one of the following: Athletics, Instinct, Intimidation, Medicine, Perception.</p>\n<p><strong>Weapon Proficiency:</strong> Pick two simple weapons or one martial weapon.</p>\n<p><strong>Background Feature:</strong> @Compendium[undertaking-homebrew.abilities.QJK4VRMK8IZWD41C]{Choose Your Battles}</p>\n<p><strong>Equipment: </strong>Pick one of the following:<ul><li>One martial weapon you are proficient with, worth up to 25gp.</li><li>A simple weapon, padded armor, and a buckler.</li></ul></p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "portion": "early"}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {}, "_id": "CQL5HS9GMYEMJ4VE", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Early Sailor", "type": "background", "img": "icons/environment/settlement/ship.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>You have dwelled near the salt and spray of the great blue sea. In this time, you learned your way around ropes and rigging, and likely got to try your hand at a tiller, sail, or perhaps even a ship's wheel. The tough work you've endured and seafaring knack you've acquired sets you apart from the uninitiated lubbers and gives you an instant rapport with other sailors.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Skill Proficiency:</strong> Pick one of the following: Acrobatics, Athletics, Instinct, Intimidation, or Perception.</p>\n<p><strong>Trade Proficiency:</strong> Pick one of the following: Artisan (Ropemaking or Woodwork), Building, Cooking, Fishing, Pathfinding, or Vehicles.</p>\n<p><strong>Background Feature:</strong> @Compendium[undertaking-homebrew.abilities.6S8K0D2XXAKPWE4J]{Know the Ropes}</p>\n<p><strong>Equipment: </strong>Pick one of the following: A cooking kit, pathfinding kit, a carpentry kit, or fishing kit.</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "portion": "early"}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {}, "_id": "1YO6NDDY6HX07DW3", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
